		<h1>Look years younger with the very latest in non-surgical Cosmetic treatments.</h1>
<h3>A short time in your own home or Clinic is all you need to look younger, prettier and your self-esteem lifted instantaneously.</h3>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><img width="150" border="0" src="http://mobile-rejuvenate.co.uk/images/stories/Restylane%20image%205.jpg" align="left" /> <br /></td>
<td>
<p>I am a qualified Registered General Nurse with a BSc (Hons) degree in Nursing. I have been a nurse for more than 20 years, a Nurse Practitioner working at an advanced level and an Independent Nurse Prescriber. I have undergone extensive training given by Harley street plastic surgeons and Nurses in the industry via the companies who make the products, attending conferences and regular training programmes covering all areas of facial and body treatments. I have completed training in advanced injection techniques in Botulinum toxins, dermal fillers, cosmeceutical skin ranges and medical skin peels to master class standard. I have developed a passion for skin health and aim to achieve the best outcome for each client.</p>
<p>I have formed two companies entitled Rejuvenate and Confident smile.</p>
<p><br />Moreover, I have successfully completed the Certified Courses and I am now a qualified Aesthetic Nurse Prescribing Practitioner. I  am committed to keeping abreast of developments in the aesthetic field and attend regular updates in advanced techniques. I am continually assessing evidence based products and treatments available, to offer men and women, to improve skin health and maintain fresher, firmer skin, all of which have wonderful anti-ageing effects. The Nursing and Midwifery Council (NMC) and the MHRA, closely monitor Aesthetic Nursing practice and currently advise now that nurses who are qualified in prescribing medicines can provide you with anti-wrinkle injections with Botox treatment product. Prescribing Nurses are governed by Medicines Management and NMC code of practice to maintain high evidence based standards of safe and quality practice. I am based in Bradford, West Yorkshire and offer a mobile service covering West Yorkshire and beyond.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h4>My goals are to provide a professional, individualised, trusting safe and client centred environment. My goals will be achieved by doing the following:-<br /><br /></h4>
<table border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<ul>
<li>Mandatory pre individualised treatment Consultation </li>
<li><strong>Face to face consultation </strong>is necessary for any treatments, skin assessment tools are used to assess appropriate skin treatments and a bespoke individualised treatment plan agreed on.</li>
<li>Initial consultation fee of £30 which will be deducted from cost of treatment and will secure your appointment. </li>
<li>Post 5 day Courtesy call</li>
<li>21 day follow up after care service (free) </li>
<li>Can provide treatments in the comfort of your own home or at my clinic. </li>
<li>I have full malpractice insurance.</li>
<li>Independent and Supplementary Prescriber.</li>
<li>Governed by NMC,MHRA for upmost safety for patients.</li>
<li>Evidence based practice.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>We regularly organise clinics and would appreciate hearing from other Hair and Beauty salons who are interested in providing a monthly Rejuvenate clinic at their premises in new areas we do not yet service.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Ever thought "how can I get £100 towards Rejuvenates treatments for free?" we have the answer; book a rejuvenate party with a minimum of 5 paying guests and your treatment will be free of charge.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Please  call </strong><strong><a href="tel:07933349773">07933 349773</a> / <a href="tel:01274603931">01274 603931</a> </strong><strong>email </strong><strong><a href="mailto:info@mobile-rejuvenate.co.uk">info@mobile-rejuvenate.co.uk</a> </strong><strong>for further details.</strong></p>
</td>
<td><img width="150" style="float: right; border: 0;" border="0" src="http://mobile-rejuvenate.co.uk/images/stories/carron.jpg" align="right" /> <br /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p> </p>
