<td><img width="100%" border="0" src="http://mobile-rejuvenate.co.uk/images/stories/IMG_7139.PNG" /></td>
<td>
<h4>My primary goal is to build a good rapport with my customers helping them to feel at ease and happy with the treatment they have obtained. To this end, customer satisfaction is paramount to me and I hope that all my customers will appreciate my attention to detail in any treatment they receive. Client referrals and 'word of mouth' are key to our business reputation and to our business growth<span style="font-family: Tahoma; font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-size: 10pt">.</span></span></h4>
